AIDA Marketing Strategy
Mobile Phones & Tablet Devices - 

ATTENTION-
Platform: YouTube, Instagram, Facebook
Demographic: Every age group, intelligent targeting, Celeb face
Interest: Brand, Upcoming mobile, Current product user
Content: Video ads, Display ads

INTEREST-
Platform: YouTube, Instagram, Facebook
Demographic: Captions, Product highlights, Celeb promotion
Interest: Model, Look, Features, Flash sales
Content: Video ads, Promotion ads

DESIRE-
Platform: YouTube, Instagram, Facebook
Demographic: Captions, Product highlights
Interest: Needs, Product qualities
Content: Video ads, Display ads

ACTION-
Platform: YouTube, Instagram, Facebook
Demographic: Captions, Product highlights
Interest: Simple Buying option, Simple cart
Content: Video ads, Display ads
